docs.text: Definition of parameters ¶ Target : It is a prediction variable of the dataset. Attack Columns : The features that are intentionally varied to cause the model to make a mistake Population Size : Number of variation tried in each iteration Exploitation Factor : Higher exploitation factor causes more smarter variations Mutation Factor : Higher mutation factor causes more random variations
